                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">He also</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
PLEADED GUILTY</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">to having been before convicted at Chelmsford in July, in the name of Edwin Smith, when he was sentenced to Seven Years' Penal Servitude</hi>.—**<hi rend="italic">
