                  <hi rend="italic">con<lb></lb>sidered that great praise was due to the officer <persName id="t18780624-name-161">
                        <interp inst="t18780624-name-161" type="gender" value="indeterminate"></interp>Martle</persName> for his courage and energy</hi>.</p>
